node.text:
The @contitourgold is BACK💫

Following the World Relays earlier this year, we’re returning to Silesia for the @memorial_kamili_skolimowskiej 🌪

Watch LIVE at 16:50 CEST Sunday Sep 5th on the World Athletics YouTube channel 🎥

#ContinentalTourGold #Athletics #TrackAndField #Track

#Athletics #TrackAndField

"It was my first #DiamondLeague experience and to be able to win against such a strong field is great!"

📷 @matthewquine / @diamondleagueathletics
